\item $X \xrightarrow[x \mapsto \circ]{f} \mathbb{R}$ everything is mapped to a point. $f^{-1}(\emptyset) = \emptyset$, $f^{-1}(\{0\}) = X$, induced topology $= \{\emptyset, X \}$.  
